1) Fetch and render the todos (Cf: api/todos)
    - The first input is a select, allowing to choose an icon amongst 3 (Cf. assets)
    - The second input is a textArea, allowing to enter a description
    - The save button allow to save the todo
    - The delete button allow to remove the todo

2) Create an empty todo at the beginning of the list, allowing to create new todos
    - On save, if all the fields are completed, a new todo is added at the beginning of the list
